# 🧠 NeuroPlay Arcade

A collection of interactive browser games powered by logic, strategy, and AI-inspired systems.

Built fully from scratch using **HTML, CSS, JavaScript, and Python (for sound generation)** — no external libraries or APIs.

---

##  Games Included

###  4 in a Row (Connect 4)
- Minimax AI with Alpha-Beta pruning
- Multiple difficulty levels
- Move history + AI analysis panel

###  Pop It (Misère Game)
- Strategic one-row gameplay
- AI using game theory (nim logic)
- Turn-based constraints and analysis

###  Dots & Boxes
- Classic grid-based strategy game
- PvP and AI modes
- Dynamic board sizes

---

##  Features

-  Smart AI opponents (Minimax + heuristics)
-  Multiple game modes (PvP & AI)
-  Real-time stats and analysis panels
-  Custom-generated sound effects (Python)
-  Fully offline — no dependencies
-  Clean modern UI

